The following package should be installed before RainbruRPG is installed:

* Boost.Test 1.34
  + Needed for unit tests
  + homepage:
    http://boost.org
  + download:
    http::/sourceforge.net/projects/boost/files/

* Freetype 9.18
  + Needed.
  + homepage:
    http://freetype.org
  + download:
    http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=3157

* Ogre3D 1.6.4 
  + Needed.
  + homepage:
    http://www.ogre3d.org
  + download:
    http://www.ogre3d.org/download

* Plugin Landscape Scene Manager 2
  + Needed
  + homepage:
    http://www.ogre3d.org/wiki/index.php/Paging_Scene_Manager
  + download:
    Can be found in the Ogre3D cvs repository

* OIS 1.2.0
  + Needed
  + homepage:
    http::/sourceforge.net/projects/wgois/
  + download:
    http::/sourceforge.net/projects/wgois/files/

* FoxToolkit 1.6
  + Needed
  + homepage:
  http://fox-toolkit.org
  + download:
  http://fox-toolkit.org/download.html

* Libcurl 7.15
  + Needed
  + homepage:
    http://curl.haxx.se
  + download:
    http://curl.haxx.se/download.html

* Boost.Filesystem 1.34
  + homepage:
    http://boost.org
  + download:
    http::/sourceforge.net/projects/boost/files/
  
* Boost.Thread 1.34
  + homepage:
    http://boost.org
  + download:
    http::/sourceforge.net/projects/boost/files/

* Boost.Serialization 1.34
  + homepage:
    http://boost.org
  + download:
    http::/sourceforge.net/projects/boost/files/

* Enet 1.1
  + homepage:
    http://enet.bespin.org
  + download:
    http://enet.bespin.org/SourceDistro.html

* Glib 2.0
  + homepage:
    http://www.gtk.org
  + download:
    http://www.gtk.org/download.html

* libsigc++ 2.0
  + homepage:
    http://libsigc.sourceforge.net
  + download:
    http://libsigc.sourceforge.net/stable.shtml

* GD 2.0
  + homepage:
    http://www.libgd.org
  + download:
    http://www.libgd.org/Downloads

* Gnet 2.0
  + homepage:
    http://live.gnome.org/GNetLibrary
  + download:
    http://ftp.gnome.org/pub/GNOME/sources/gnet/2.0/

* Libmagic 4.26
  + Recommended 
    Needed to build the game server.
  + homepage:
    http://darwinsys.com/file  
  + download:
    ftp://ftp.astron.com/pub/file/

* Cppunit 1.12
  + Recommended.
    Needed to be able to build unit tests.
  + homepage:
    http://apps.sourceforge.net/mediawiki/cppunit/
  + download:
    http://sourceforge.net/projects/cppunit/files/

* dot 2.20.2
  + Recommended.
    Needed to produce graphs in documentation.
  + homepage:
    http://www.graphviz.org/
  + download:
    http://www.graphviz.org/Download..php